'''模拟经营游戏'''是[[模拟游戏|模拟游戏]]的一种。由玩家扮演管理者的角色，对游戏中虚拟的现实世界进行[[经营管理|经营管理]]。可以是城市，可以是国家，可以是世界，可以是公司，可以是其他团体。虚拟经营游戏一般模拟现实社会的模式，人物的想法等都是根据规则[[随机|随机]]定制的。许多模拟经营游戏以“大亨(Tycoon)”一词作为结尾。常见游戏的目标是彻底控制游戏中可控制的所有资源，实现[[垄断|垄断]]；或者发展到一定程度（例如足够科技水平带领市民脱离地球）。

== 現實世界中的應用 ==

由於經濟仿真模擬真實世界的系統，他們往往可以被用於經濟學教育，允許學生在現實生活中遇到他們之前體驗和測試自己的情況<ref name=ssl>{{cite book | last = Farkas | first = Meredith | title = Social Software in Libraries: Building Collaboration, Communication, and Community Online | publisher = [[Information_Today,_Inc.|Information Today, Inc.]] | year = 2007 | accessdate = 2008-06-18 | isbn =1-57387-275-X|url=http://books.google.com/?id=AlARogbZHqcC&pg=PA216&dq=%22economic+simulation%22+game | page=216}}</ref> ，允許學生實驗和測試假設<ref name=dkskrht>{{cite journal | last = Thole | first = Heinz-Jürgen | coauthors = Claus Möbus, Olaf Schröder | title = Domain Knowledge Structure, Knowledge Representation and Hypotheses Testing | journal = Artificial Intelligence in Education: Knowledge and Media in Learning | pages = 410 | publisher = [[IOS_Press|IOS Press]] | year = 1997 | url = http://books.google.com/?id=9L4reNbo7MQC&pg=PA410&dq=%22economic+simulation%22+game | isbn = 978-90-5199-353-0}}</ref>，也比被動地從黑板授課時的主體看起來更“真實”<ref name=dyn_ss>{{cite book | last = Schurr | first = Sandra | title = Dynamite in the Classroom: A How-to Handbook for Teachers | publisher = [[National_Middle_School_Association|National Middle School Association]] | year = 1994 | url = http://books.google.com/?id=HK_uqW_oS7EC&pg=PA73&dq=economic+simulation+game| isbn = 1-56090-041-5 | page = 73}}</ref>。他們也廣泛使用於培訓員工和學習如何管理<ref>{{cite book|author=李广龙|title=快乐管理|year=2002|publisher=中信出版社|isbn=9787800735400}}</ref> <ref name=udg>{{cite book | last = Rutter | first = Jason | coauthors = Jo Bryce | title = Understanding Digital Games | publisher = [[Sage_Publications,_Inc.|Sage Publications, Inc.]] | year = 2006 | isbn = 1-4129-0033-6|url=http://books.google.com/?id=Ji3baoCZL8gC&pg=PA227&dq=%22economic+simulation%22+game|page=227}}</ref>，並研究經濟模型，甚至被用在經濟模擬實驗和研究消費者的行為<ref name=vetl_lcj>{{cite book | last = Jain | first = L. C. | coauthors = R. J. Howlett, N. S. Ichalkaranje, G. Tonfoni | title = virtual environments for teaching & learning | publisher = [[World_Scientific|World Scientific]] | year = 2002 | url = http://books.google.com/?id=gDPbGslq1LoC&pg=PA20&dq=%22economic+simulation%22+game | isbn = 981-238-167-8 | page = 20}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==

最早期的经营模拟游戏於1983年發布，並獲得[[藝電|藝電]]的獎項，但它只銷售了30000份。<ref name=hs_mule>{{cite book | last = DeMaria | first = Rusel | coauthors = Johnny L. Wilson | title = High Score!: The Illustrated History of Electronic Games | publisher = [[McGraw-Hill_Professional|McGraw-Hill Professional]] | year = 2004 | pages = 174–175 | isbn = 0-07-223172-6|url=http://books.google.com/?id=HJNvZLvpCEQC&pg=PA174&dq=%22economic+simulation%22+game}}</ref>同年，[[Epyx|Epyx]]發布了《[[石油大亨|石油大亨]]》。

近几年，[[网絡游戏|网絡游戏]]迅速发展，涌向了一批模拟经营类的网絡游戏，《超级富豪》、《足球大亨》、《厨师小当家》等也屬此類。

